<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-220-504  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 220 504.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  April 24 1989 v6 n16 p29(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Color scanner accurate enough for medical, engineering needs.andO;(American Data Systems Inc.'s Graphex scanner) (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Gianatasio, David.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   American Data Systems Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   American Data Systems Graphex (Scanning device) (productintroduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionScanningColorFunctional Capabilities.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Color Scanner Accurate Enough For Medical, Engineering NeedsandM;YONKERS, N.Y.andP;  -- American Data Systems has announced a flatbed color scannerthat company officials said provides a faster and more efficient way todigitize full color or black-and-white images.andM;Available for 11-by-17-inch image input, the Graphex scanner features 12 bitplanes of color in its analog-to-digital conversion, ensuring usable8-bit-plane-per-color output capability or 256 gray levels per color.andM;This ability, officials said, results in highly accurate images, making theunit suitable for medical, engineering, scientific and graphic artsapplications.andM;For black-and-white images, the scanner provides either 256-level gray scaleor pure black-and-white binary scanning for type or line art.andM;The unit comes with a 15-inch color monitor that keeps users informed ofscanning progress at all times.andM;Originals can be produced in either transparent or reflective format in 81/2-by-11 1/2-inch sizes.andM;Also, users can define specific image areas of any size for scanning.andP;  Smallareas can be magnified as many as four times.andM;The scanner is connected to a computer via a SCSI port and uses a singlecharge coupled device (CCD) laser array to scan images.andM;Prices for the Graphex scanner range from $20,000 to $60,000, depending onthe output size.andM;Output size can vary from 8 1/2-by-11 1/2 to 11 1/2-by-17 inches or larger,official said.andM;American Data Systems Inc. is located at 4 Executive Plaza, Yonkers, NY10701, (914) 375-1200.andO;</TEXT></DOC>